tests.title: should check and uncheck checkboxes
tests.fullTitle: Automation Practice Test Suite should check and uncheck checkboxes
tests.code:
// Working with checkboxes
cy.get(_support_pageObjects_selectors_json__WEBPACK_IMPORTED_MODULE_0__.checkBoxOption1).check().should('be.checked').and('have.value', 'option1').and('have.attr', 'type', 'checkbox'); //check checkbox
cy.get(_support_pageObjects_selectors_json__WEBPACK_IMPORTED_MODULE_0__.checkBoxOption1).uncheck().should('not.be.checked'); //Uncheck
cy.get(_support_pageObjects_selectors_json__WEBPACK_IMPORTED_MODULE_0__.checkboxes).check(['option2', 'option3']); // Multiple checkboxes
